Now, I don't remember the name of our waitress unfortunately, but she was the one that brought us our bottles of mascato and the food hmmmmmm. This lady was point and never let our glasses go empty despite the amount of people in the venue. The lamb and the moi moi lol...The plaintains....Now I only have 2 qualms. First, I know they were called LAMB BITES, but they were a little dry. Tasty and Flavorful but dry. Second, can somebody get a mop in the mens bathroom at some point in the night lol. But that's it.
